==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: chóngshān jùnlĭng

===Etymology===
From the [[wikisource:Preface to the Poems Composed at the Orchid Pavilion|Preface to the Poems Composed at the Orchid Pavilion]], by [[wikipedia:Wang Xizhi|Wang Xizhi]] (王羲之).

===Idiom===
'''[[崇山]][[峻岭]]'''

# high mountains and lofty peaks.

===Related terms===
*[[茂林修竹]]

===Alternate forms===
[[崇山峻嶺]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
*[[崇]][[山]][[峻]][[領]] (as seen in [[wikisource:Preface to the Poems Composed at the Orchid Pavilion|Preface to the Poems Composed at the Orchid Pavilion]])

